
这是抓取windows平台桌面屏幕和摄像头图像，以及音频的远程控制程序。
可以在各个平台的浏览器中直接进行控制，
支持的浏览器包括 chrome，firefox， safari， opera， Microsoft Edge等，（不支持IE，对IE11只是有限支持)
被控制端支持的平台包括 windows系列（从 XP，WIN7， WIN8， WIN10）。

也支持原生的客户端程序，只是本次没有把客户端提供出来。

这个就跟类似NoVNC的远程控制一样，在HTML5页面中进行远程控制，
但是在windows平台，这个软件功能更多些，不但提供音频，提供摄像头远程浏览，
还提供服务器中转解决内网访问等问题, 同时能把多台被控制机器集中到一起，对于维护人员来说有一定好处。


bin目录包含xdisp_virt.exe程序，xdisp_virt.ini是它的配置文件，
xdisp_server.exe程序，xdisp_server.ini是它的配置文件。
配置文件有详细的每个字段说明。
已经配置成默认设置，可以直接运行exe程序。

driver目录是镜像驱动，没有签名。

html目录包含所有网页以及javascript脚本，html目录已经被打包进 xdisp_virt.exe程序。

image目录是程序运行的一些效果图。

相关博客：
http://blog.csdn.net/fanxiushu/article/details/78869719

(English):
This is a remote control program that grabs the desktop and camera images of the windows platform, as well as audio.
It can be controlled directly in the browsers of each platform,
Supported browsers include chrome, Firefox, Safari, opera, Microsoft Edge, etc. (no support for IE, limited support for IE11)
The platforms supported by the controlled side include the windows series (from XP, WIN7, WIN8, WIN10).

It also supports native client programs, but this time the client is not provided.
This is a remote control in a HTML5 page, like NoVNC - like remote control,
But on the windows platform, the software is more functional, providing not only audio, but also camera remote browsing.
It also provides server transfer to solve internal network access and other problems, 
and can concentrate multiple controlled machines together. 
It has some benefits for the maintenance personnel.


The bin directory contains the xdisp_virt.exe program, and xdisp_virt.ini is its configuration file.
The xdisp_server.exe program, xdisp_server.ini is its configuration file.
The configuration file has a detailed description of each field.
It has been configured as a default setting to run the EXE program directly.

The driver directory is mirrored and has no signature.

The HTML directory contains all the web pages and JavaScript scripts, 
and the HTML directory has been packed into the xdisp_virt.exe program.

The image directory is some effect diagram of the program running.

for detail:
http://blog.csdn.net/fanxiushu/article/details/78869719

Fanxiushu 2017
